oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Urusula, Emmett, and Michael - Demo Tapes
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of four demo tracks by an unidentified group. The information lists the recording artists as Urusula, Emmett, and Michael. The recordings took place during the December of 1976.
